<i>Wakuwaku wo hyakubai ni shite</i>

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:42.590
<i>paatii no shuyaku ni narou.</i>

00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:49.760
<i>Muchuu ni nareru mono ga</i>

00:00:49.970 --> 00:00:55.560
<i>itsuka kimi wo sugee
yatsu ni suru n da.</i>

00:00:55.770 --> 00:00:58.310
<i>NO... TEN P-KAN.</i>

00:00:58.520 --> 00:01:00.940
<i>Sora wa harete</i>

00:01:01.150 --> 00:01:03.900
<i>lPPAl OPPAI.</i>

00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:06.410
<i>Boku genki.</i>

00:01:06.610 --> 00:01:09.580
<i>Toraburu to asobe</i>

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:12.330
<i>yancha booi.</i>

00:01:12.530 --> 00:01:15.150
<i>We Gotta Power!</i>

00:01:15.370 --> 00:01:21.000
